<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para><db:link xlink:href="qt3danimation-qanimationgroup.xml">Qt3DAnimation::QAnimationGroup</db:link> class is used to group multiple animations so that they can act as one animation. The position set to the group is also set to all animations in a group. The duration is the maximum of the individual animations. The animations can be any supported animation type and do not have to have the same name.</db:para>
</db:section>
